@node "About" "About This File"

  @{b}About the DCBoT Spoilers@{ub}
  Initial release, version 0.5.

These spoilers are the result of many people's contributions over a period
of many months. We believe them to be accurate as of ADOM version
0.9.9gamma6, but there may be inaccuracies due to rapid changes due to game
development, bad research, or just plain human (or dwarvish, elvish,
orcish, you get the idea) error. The Drakalor Chain Board of Tourism is not
responsible for any character deaths, maiming, close calls, or other
terrible things that might happen when using this information, whether the
information given is correct or not.

In many places, the version variations have been noted, especially where
new items or skills have been introduced.
If you have contributions or corrections to make to these spoilers, please
contact Richard Fowler, thinker@texas.net In this first release, many
things are not included which are known, but time constraints did not allow
their inclusion before release.
